#: ui/main.qml:29
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"Legacy X11 apps with global shortcuts and other features accessed while "
"running in the background need to be able to listen for keystrokes all the "
"time.<nl/><nl/>If you use any of these apps, you can choose your preferred "
"balance of security and compatibility here."
msgstr ""
"Les aplicacions X11 antigues amb dreceres globals i altres funcions a les "
"quals s'accedix mentre s'executen en segon pla han de ser capaces d'escoltar "
"les pulsacions de tecla tot el temps.<nl/><nl/>Si utilitzeu alguna d'estes "
"aplicacions, podeu triar ací el balanç preferit entre seguretat i "
"compatibilitat."

#: ui/main.qml:50
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:group"
msgid "Listening for keystrokes:"
msgstr "Escoltament de pulsacions de tecla:"

#: ui/main.qml:57
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:radio Listening for keystrokes is prohibited"
msgid "Prohibited"
msgstr "Prohibit"

#: ui/main.qml:73
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid "Most secure; global shortcuts will not work in X11 apps"
msgstr ""
"El més segur, les dreceres globals no funcionaran a les aplicacions X11"

#: ui/main.qml:87
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:radio Listening for keystrokes is allowed for…"
msgid "Only the Meta, Control, Alt, and Shift keys"
msgstr "Només les tecles «Meta», «Control», «Alt» i «Majúscules»"

#: ui/main.qml:103
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"High security; push-to-talk and other modifier-only global shortcuts will "
"work in X11 apps"
msgstr ""
"Alta seguretat; només funcionaran les dreceres globals prémer per a parlar i "
"altres modificadors a les aplicacions X11"

#: ui/main.qml:117
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:radio Listening for keystrokes is allowed for…"
msgid ""
"As above, plus any key pressed while the Control, Alt, or Meta key is also "
"pressed"
msgstr ""
"Com l'anterior, a més de qualsevol tecla premuda mentre també es premen les "
"tecles «Control», «Alt» o «Meta»"

#: ui/main.qml:133
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid "Moderate security; all global shortcuts will work in X11 apps"
msgstr ""
"Seguretat moderada; totes les dreceres globals funcionaran a les aplicacions "
"X11"

#: ui/main.qml:147
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:radio Listening for keystrokes is always allowed"
msgid "Always allowed"
msgstr "Sempre permeses"

#: ui/main.qml:163
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"Least secure; all X11 apps will be able to see any text you type into any "
"application"
msgstr ""
"Menys segur; totes les aplicacions X11 podran veure qualsevol text que "
"teclegeu en qualsevol aplicació"

#: ui/main.qml:177
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"Note that using this setting will reduce system security and permit "
"malicious software to steal passwords and spy on the text that you type. "
"Make sure you understand and accept this risk."
msgstr ""
"Cal tindre en compte que l'ús d'este paràmetre reduirà la seguretat del "
"sistema i permetrà que programari maliciós robe contrasenyes i espie el text "
"que escriviu. Assegureu-vos que enteneu i accepteu este risc."

#: ui/main.qml:193
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:group"
msgid "Listening for mouse buttons:"
msgstr "Escoltament dels botons del ratolí:"

#: ui/main.qml:199
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:radio Listening for mouse buttons is allowed"
msgid "Allowed"
msgstr "Permés"

#: ui/main.qml:215
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"Moderate security; global shortcuts involving mouse buttons will work in X11 "
"apps"
msgstr ""
"Seguretat moderada; totes les dreceres globals que involucren botons del "
"ratolí funcionaran a les aplicacions X11"

#: ui/main.qml:233
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:group"
msgid "Control of pointer and keyboard:"
msgstr "Control del punter i del teclat:"

#: ui/main.qml:240
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"@option:check Allowed control of pointer and keyboard without asking for "
"permissions for allowed apps"
msgid "Allowed apps"
msgstr "Aplicacions permeses"

#: ui/main.qml:246
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button"
msgid "See Allowed Applications…"
msgstr "Veure les aplicacions permeses…"

#: ui/main.qml:259
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"Moderate security; XWayland-using apps claiming to be something on this list "
"will be able to take control of the computer, because XWayland-using apps’ "
"identities can’t be verified"
msgstr ""
"Seguretat moderada; les aplicacions que utilitzen XWayland que afirmen ser "
"alguna cosa en esta llista podran prendre el control de l'ordinador, perquè "
"les identitats de les aplicacions que utilitzen XWayland no es poden "
"verificar"

#: ui/main.qml:272
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"@option:radio Allow control of pointer and keyboard without asking for "
"permission"
msgid "Allow without asking for permission"
msgstr "Permet sense demanar permís"

#: ui/main.qml:283
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid "Least secure; all X11 apps will be able to take control of the computer"
msgstr ""
"Menys segur; totes les aplicacions X11 podran prendre el control de "
"l'ordinador"

#: ui/main.qml:295
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"@title:window title of the page opened by the 'See allowed applications' "
"button"
msgid "Applications allowed to control the pointer and keyboard"
msgstr "Aplicacions permeses a controlar el punter i el teclat"

#: ui/main.qml:315
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip %1 is the name of the app/binary"
msgid "Do not allow %1 to control the pointer and keyboard without asking"
msgstr "No permetes que %1 controle el punter i el teclat sense preguntar"

#: ui/main.qml:329
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"Note that using this setting will drastically reduce system security and "
"permit malicious software to take complete control of your pointer and "
"keyboard. Make sure you understand and accept this risk."
msgstr ""
"Cal tindre en compte que l'ús d'este paràmetre reduirà dràsticament la "
"seguretat del sistema i permetrà que programari maliciós prenga un control "
"complet del punter i del teclat. Assegureu-vos que enteneu i accepteu este "
"risc."
